column2: What is the tokenomics behind the protocol.
column3: The primary feature of the Farmfactory application is to provide incentives for users who hold your token. Users purchase and stake your token, earning rewards in return. This process does not cause a decrease in the value of your token. You do not earn revenue directly from the application, but rather it is your users who earn revenue through the rewards they receive. The APY earned by users depends on the number of deposits, the number of users, and the amount of tokens they have staked.
